on the backend. Current defaults expose `exa_search`, `exa_answer`, `serper_google_search`, `parallel_search`, and `bash`.\n- The `bash` tool runs in an isolated in-memory workspace and lazily exposes `/refs/prompts.json` for GTM prompt-template lookup.\n- Tool calls reuse Deepline tool execution paths where possible.\n","format":"markdown","kind":"action","operation":"deeplineagent","source":"native","inputs":[],"outputs":[]}]}
